text: Wyoming is a 1940 American western movie directed by Richard Thorpe and starring Wallace Berry, Leo Carrillo, Ann Rutherford, Lee Bowman, Chill Wills, Henry Travers. It was distributed by Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer. ==Other websites== * Wyoming at the Internet Movie Database Category:1940 movies Category:1940s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by Richard Thorpe
